    subs2vec Project Model and Frequency Data Downloads

    subsData.Rd

    Dataset to use the import_subs function to import subtitle fastText model outputs and frequency counts. Includes information about matching `udpipe` models for tagging.

    Usage

    data(subsData)

    Format

    A data frame of links and information about the subs2vec project.

    • language_codethe two letter language code of the model

    • subs_veca link to download the subtitle only fastText model

    • subs_counta link to download the frequencies for the tokens in the subtitle data

    • wiki_veca link to download the wikipedia only fastText model

    • wiki_counta link to download the frequencies for the tokens in the wikipedia data

    • filesthe number of files in the OpenSubtitles data

    • tokensthe number of tokens in the OpenSubtitles data

    • sentencesthe number of sentences in the OpenSubtitles data

    • languagethe full name of the language for reference

    • udpipe_modelthe matching `udpipe` model for download to parse tokens
